About us
Four Green Fields is proud to offer great Irish food and the freshest pints of Guinness in the region 365 days a year. Four Green Fields has been voted by the Dublin-based publication "Ireland of the Welcomes" as one the top 10 Irish pubs in the world. Four Green Fields was also named one of the top 100 places in America to drink beer by Imbibe magazine.

Gas Worx Events
Luxury Tequila & Caviar Tasting
Thursday September 11th
Sunday may 8th
We are excited to announce an exclusive tasting event featuring 12 exquisite tequilas paired with  Golden Goat gourmet caviar and delicious appetizers. This event will showcase the art of tequila tasting and the culinary delights that complement it. Join us for an evening of exploration and indulgence.
Featuring
Tears of Llorona
Corralejo Gran Reserve Añejo
Corralejo 1821 Extra Añejo
AsomBroso Silver
AsomBroso Eros Reposado
AsomBroso 5 Year Old Extra Añejo
Dulce Vida Ochos Años
Dulce Vida Lone Star Ed
Dulce Vida Lone Star Añejo
Reserva de la Familia Reposado
Reserva de la Familia Extra Añejo
Reserva de la Familia Cristalino
06:00 PM - 10:00 PM
